article_text:
The Palin effect in Texas

Photo: Congressional Quarterly, Getty Images UNITED STATES - JANUARY 18 - Former Alaska Gov. Sarah Palin speaks...

One of the overlooked constants in politics, especially in Texas politics, is that pundits' use of the term "tea party" to mean a single monolith of right-wing voters is hardly ever apt.
